Vous vous sentez endormi, fatigué ?

32
00:09:25,226 --> 00:09:35,596
Eh bien, redressez la colonne, ouvrez les yeux, levez-vous.

33
00:09:35,616 --> 00:09:42,102
As we begin to feel more focused, see if you can draw closer to the breath.

34
